4. Troubleshooting & Security Basics
21. What is ping?
Ping checks connectivity between two devices.
22. What is ipconfig?
Command used in Windows to check IP configuration.
23. What will you do if internet is not working?
Check cable → Check IP → Restart router → Ping gateway → Contact ISP.
24. What is APIPA?
APIPA (169.254.x.x) is assigned when DHCP fails.
25. What is the difference between public and private IP?
Public IP is used on internet.
Private IP is used inside local network.
26. What is HTTPS?
HTTPS is secure HTTP using encryption.
27. What is VPN?
VPN creates secure encrypted connection over internet.
